2026-05-03T23:02:29.7059578Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-03T23:02:29.7060493Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-03T23:02:29.7061421Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-03T23:02:29.7062355Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
